01:12:08.203 --> 01:12:09.246
"More?

01:12:10.080 --> 01:12:11.164
"She's a traitor."

01:12:16.753 --> 01:12:19.214
"No! By my life!

01:12:19.756 --> 01:12:21.800
"Privy to none of this!

01:12:22.843 --> 01:12:25.596
"How will this grieve you

01:12:25.679 --> 01:12:28.473
